# Terraform — state can hold sensitive values and is kept in S3, not here.
# terraform.tfvars IS committed on purpose: it holds no secrets, and the CI
# plan/apply jobs need it (github_owner/github_repo have no defaults, and
# create_github_oidc_provider must stay false). Never put secrets in it.
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
